PrecisOrder giving notice of the National Guideline for ADHESIVES (ECP-44-92) specifying that certified products must not be formulated with aromatic solvents, borax, formaldehyde, halogenated solvents or compounds of mercury, lead cadmium and hexavalent chromium and limiting the amount of volatile organic compounds (VOCs) within the product formulation to 20.0 g/Litre.
